	   <tr><td colspan=2>Same skill. I forget the lvl DE's get to start.  Mine never went up until I past 35th lvl.  Found boat rides to be great for raising hide skill.  You hide skill check is made boat moves and unhides you.  Just click the button whenever you can.<br>Even with the skill maxed for an SK at 75 it doesn't work very often.  When you hide you will almost always see yourself dissappear.  That doesn't mean that everybody else sees you dissappear.  Only real way to know if it worked is see if something wandering by aggroes on you or not.<br>&nbsp;<br>The Power of Hate conquers all foes.</td></tr>
