	   <tr><td colspan=2>Actually their are two ways to use hide:<br><br>1) Con something (anything) that does not con &quot;indifferant&quot; to you.  Try to hide.  Recheck the con, if its indifferant you have hidden successfully.  If not, click it off, wait for it to recycle and try again.<br><br>2) Summon your pet (9th+ level here obviously) and then keep trying to hide until the pet commits suicide.  Your pet will die when you have successfully hidden.<br><br>Special Note: Do not sit and meditate (or even just sit) until AFTER you know you are hidden.  Otherwise by sitting you increase the range at which mobs will aggro you, and make even so that stuff that would normally leave you alone (ie. con/green stuff) will attack.  Once you are hidden, its fine, just don't move until you are done healing/medding.<br>&nbsp;<br>Kadia Coldnight<br>Tier'dal Shadowknight<br>Saryrn Server</td></tr>
