	   <tr><td colspan=2>I was able to beat a 30th necro when I was 30th mainly due to the fact I switched to my 1hs and shield. I created pet he engaged the necros pet while I feared then I darknessed the necro so he couldn't run. Everytime he began to cast I bashed 8 of ten times he was interupted. I life tapped him between swings and when he was half health I HT'd bam dead necro. Now if he had had his SS up it would have been different story. The key to beating a necro is good resist items and interupting his spells as much as possible. Remember to stock up pumice stones and dispell his DoT's.<br>&nbsp;<br>Cannis Skywise 47 Ranger<br>Razer Darkreaver 42st Sk<br>Jeetkundo 20th Monk<br>Mikaraz 26th Warrior</td></tr>
