	   <tr><td colspan=2>My .02 worth on weaps for SKs.  I took my troll to lvl 20 with 1HS, mostly because I was building Bash.  By lvl 20 he was over 100 in 1HS and Bash skills.  At lvl 20 velium weaps start to proc, and they are widely available from merchants and players for relatively little, and it's fun to have a weapon proc after all that waiting--so I got a Velium Battle Axe for 20 PP from a player.<br><br>At 22 I bought a Stalag Terrorspine Spear (piercing) from a vendor in OT for 320 PP.  Wiped me out, but it procs Disempower.  Am now training up on that--goal is to graduate to uber weapons like Great Spear of Dawn or Narandi's Lance.  So Piercing weapons are probably the weapons of choice for me when I hit 50's and above.<br><br>Finally: I trained this char on Archery from the start, ditto Fletching.  Reason: great pulling w/out wasting mana, can sell crafted bows and arrows for decent cash, make good presents when trying to buy friends (since nobody likes Troll SKs).  At 27 and skill 120 my troll can usually hit for 15-20 w/ shaped ashwood recurve bow and class 2 arrows.<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
